  "title": "FOOD VIDEOGRAPHER / CONTENT CREATOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>Specialisation:</strong> Food & F&B Content<br /><strong>Brands:</strong> Japanese Restaurants + Lifestyle Salon<br /><strong>Location:</strong> Hybrid (WFH / Town)<br /><strong>Schedule:</strong> 5 days a week<br /><strong>Salary:</strong> Competitive package (based on experience)</p><h3>🍣 About the Role</h3><p>We’re looking for a <strong>Food Videographer / Food Content Creator</strong> with a strong eye for food styling, motion, and storytelling. This role focuses heavily on capturing food from close-up textures and plating to live kitchen moments and finished dishes.</p><p>If you enjoy shooting food that makes people hungry and understand how food content performs on Instagram and TikTok, we’d love to have you on the team.</p><h3>📌 Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Plan, shoot, and edit <strong>food-focused short-form videos</strong> for Instagram & TikTok</p></li><li><p>Capture food textures, plating details, pouring shots, grilling, slicing, and kitchen action</p></li><li><p>Work closely with chefs and service teams to stage and execute food shoots efficiently</p></li><li><p>Edit videos with music, text, and effects optimised for social platforms</p></li><li><p>Maintain visual consistency across all food-related content</p></li><li><p>Support occasional lifestyle or ambience shoots when needed</p></li><li><p>Manage content timelines and deliver independently</p></li></ul><h3>🎯 What We’re Looking For</h3><ul><li><p>Proven experience in <strong>food videography or F&B content creation</strong></p></li><li><p>Strong understanding of lighting, angles, and movement for food</p></li><li><p>Ability to shoot both <strong>static food shots and dynamic kitchen scenes</strong></p></li><li><p>Skilled in video editing (Adobe Premiere Pro, Final Cut Pro, etc.)</p></li><li><p>Familiar with Instagram & TikTok food content trends</p></li><li><p>Detail-oriented, efficient, and able to work in fast-paced restaurant environments</p></li><li><p>Open to occasional evenings or weekends for shoots</p></li></ul><h3>🌟 Why Join Us</h3><ul><li><p>AWS <strong>guaranteed</strong></p></li><li><p>Performance bonus</p></li><li><p>Staff discounts across all F&B and salon brands</p></li><li><p>Work with established Japanese restaurant brands</p></li></ul><h3>📲 How to Apply</h3><p>WhatsApp your <strong>resume, portfolio, expected salary</strong> to <strong>+65 8868 8831</strong><br /><strong>Singaporeans only.</strong><br />Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>",
